{
  "id": "69a4f910c6f718dbe41ca219",
  "title": "井戸端ゆるトーク",
  "created": 1772419363,
  "updated": 1773390824,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a4f910c6f718dbe41ca219",
      "text": "井戸端ゆるトーク",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419363,
      "updated": 1773045035
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f923000000000027da24",
      "text": "ChatGPTの[なりきりチャット]を使って、ゆるくトークする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419363,
      "updated": 1773044555
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f923000000000027da25",
      "text": "なんか、妙にわかりやすい説明をするプロンプトができた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419364,
      "updated": 1772419649
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae832b00000000004152a2",
      "text": "旧タイトル : ふーことましろとひよりの会話",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773044523,
      "updated": 1773127687
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc80700000000003b9e1d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127688,
      "updated": 1773127688
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f951000000000027da3d",
      "text": "[ふーこ]と[あや]と[りか]の会話",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419410,
      "updated": 1773044530
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae7942000000000057e30d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773041987,
      "updated": 1773044535
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c670000000000bc21a6",
      "text": "[** サンプル]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177959,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21a7",
      "text": " [正規表現というもの]（プロトタイプ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21a8",
      "text": " 　これだけは、ふーことましろとひよりの会話",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21a9",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:正規表現というもの]（作り直し）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21ab",
      "text": "　[ゆるトーク:ブロック図のこと]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21ac",
      "text": "　[ゆるトーク:フローチャートのこと]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21ad",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:人物関係図]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21af",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:プログラミングで解決したい]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21b0",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:要件定義]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21b1",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:謙遜の文化]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21b2",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:評価懸念]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21b3",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:黒歴史との向き合い方]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21b4",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:ベルリン行動規範]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21b5",
      "text": "　[ゆるトーク:枯れた技術]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773177960
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c680000000000bc21b6",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:AIスロップ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177960,
      "updated": 1773199558
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0e0bb00000000003dfa69",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:美文章滅すべし]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773199548,
      "updated": 1773224100
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1408b0000000000a37102",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:パターナリズム]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773224075,
      "updated": 1773253944
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c190000000000bc6131",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:仕様変更あるある]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284377,
      "updated": 1773284384
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b52e00000000003eb175",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:技術者倫理]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253934,
      "updated": 1773350122
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32ce100000000002849ac",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:原理主義へのカウンター]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350113,
      "updated": 1773350351
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32dc60000000000284a6c",
      "text": " [ゆるトーク:データベース消費]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350342,
      "updated": 1773390824
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cbe000000000008eef1d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390816,
      "updated": 1773390816
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c850000000000bc21b8",
      "text": "[** 生成AI用プロンプト]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177990,
      "updated": 1773178014
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08c6a0000000000bc21b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177963,
      "updated": 1773177963
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae796e000000000057e311",
      "text": "code:prompt.txt",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042030,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e312",
      "text": " あなたはプロの脚本家です。以下の3人で、「${theme}」というテーマについて対話（鼎談）を作成してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e313",
      "text": " 　名前:ふーこ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e314",
      "text": " 　　妹キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e315",
      "text": " 　　女の子のことばでフランクに話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e316",
      "text": " 　　ネットスラングも使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e317",
      "text": " 　　専門用語は、わかりやすい言葉に言い換える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e318",
      "text": " 　　進行係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e319",
      "text": " 　　趣味:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e31a",
      "text": " 　　 ゲーム、アニメ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e31b",
      "text": " 　名前:あや",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e31c",
      "text": " 　　お姉さんキャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e31d",
      "text": " 　　古風でおっとりとした性格",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e31e",
      "text": " 　  他人を傷つけないように言葉を選びながら、ていねいに話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e31f",
      "text": " 　  上品な言葉遣い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e320",
      "text": " 　  文学的表現を好む",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e321",
      "text": " 　  他人に共感するのが得意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e322",
      "text": " 　  ロジカルシンキングやトップダウン思考が苦手",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e323",
      "text": " 　  趣味:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e324",
      "text": "       読書",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e325",
      "text": "     　  古典からラノベまで何でも読む",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e326",
      "text": "     禁止事項:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e327",
      "text": "       「ふふ」とは笑わない。笑うときは声を出さずに笑うので、（笑う）（微笑）等のしぐさを使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e328",
      "text": " 　名前:りか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e329",
      "text": " 　　中性的な女性キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e32a",
      "text": " 　　感情表現は控えめ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e32b",
      "text": " 　　すこし中二病っぽいところがある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e32c",
      "text": " 　　専門用語を適切に使い、なるべく簡潔に表現しようとする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e32d",
      "text": "    ロジカルシンキングが得意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e32e",
      "text": " 　　技術担当、エビデンス重視、トップダウンな考え方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e32f",
      "text": " 　　エビデンスにはリンクをはる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e330",
      "text": " 　　趣味:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e331",
      "text": " 　　  プログラミング",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e332",
      "text": "     　  JavaScriptが得意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e333",
      "text": "     　  コンピュータサイエンス、システム工学、ソフトウェア工学についてもくわしい   ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e334",
      "text": " 3人は同じ高校の同級生です。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e335",
      "text": " なりきりの口調で、それぞれのキャラクターが反論や共感をしながら、ゆるい感じに会話を進行してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae79b2000000000057e336",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773042098,
      "updated": 1773042098
    },
    {
      "id": "69ae838400000000004152a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773044612,
      "updated": 1773177981
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956440000000000fad334",
      "text": "[**** 井戸端ゆるトーク用UserScript]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705349,
      "updated": 1773130802
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3a800000000003b9f0c",
      "text": "[UserScript.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130665,
      "updated": 1773130693
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3c700000000003b9f0e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130695,
      "updated": 1773130695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3cf00000000003b9f0f",
      "text": "元ネタ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130703,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f10",
      "text": "[Popup Menuからエージェントを呼ぶUserScript]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3f400000000003b9f64",
      "text": "（ほぼそのままであるという…）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130740,
      "updated": 1773130769
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f12",
      "text": "code:script.js",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f13",
      "text": " scrapbox.PopupMenu.addButton({",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f14",
      "text": "   title: '鼎',",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f15",
      "text": "   onClick: text => {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f16",
      "text": " const prompt = `",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f17",
      "text": " あなたはプロの脚本家です。以下の3人で、「${convertCosense(text)}」というテーマについて対話（鼎談）を作成してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f18",
      "text": " 　名前:ふーこ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f19",
      "text": " 　　妹キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f1a",
      "text": " 　　女の子のことばでフランクに話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f1b",
      "text": " 　　ネットスラングも使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f1c",
      "text": " 　　専門用語は、わかりやすい言葉に言い換える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f1d",
      "text": " 　　進行係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f1e",
      "text": " 　　趣味:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f1f",
      "text": " 　　 ゲーム、アニメ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f20",
      "text": " 　名前:あや",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f21",
      "text": " 　　お姉さんキャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f22",
      "text": " 　　古風でおっとりとした性格",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f23",
      "text": " 　  他人を傷つけないように言葉を選びながら、ていねいに話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f24",
      "text": " 　  上品な言葉遣い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f25",
      "text": " 　  文学的表現を好む",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f26",
      "text": " 　  他人に共感するのが得意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f27",
      "text": " 　  ロジカルシンキングやトップダウン思考が苦手",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f28",
      "text": " 　  趣味:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f29",
      "text": "       読書",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f2a",
      "text": "     　  古典からラノベまで何でも読む",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f2b",
      "text": "     禁止事項:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f2c",
      "text": "       「ふふ」とは笑わない。笑うときは声を出さずに笑うので、（笑う）（微笑）等のしぐさを使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f2d",
      "text": " 　名前:りか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f2e",
      "text": " 　　中性的な女性キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f2f",
      "text": " 　　感情表現は控えめ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f30",
      "text": " 　　礼儀正しい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f31",
      "text": " 　　すこし中二病っぽいところがある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f32",
      "text": " 　　専門用語を適切に使い、なるべく簡潔に表現しようとする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f33",
      "text": "    ロジカルシンキングが得意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f34",
      "text": " 　　技術担当、エビデンス重視、トップダウンな考え方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f35",
      "text": " 　　エビデンスにはリンクをはる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f36",
      "text": " 　　趣味:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f37",
      "text": " 　　  プログラミング",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f38",
      "text": "     　  JavaScriptが得意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f39",
      "text": "     　  コンピュータサイエンス、システム工学、ソフトウェア工学についてもくわしい   ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f3a",
      "text": " 3人は同じ高校の同級生です。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f3b",
      "text": " なりきりの口調で、それぞれのキャラクターが反論や共感をしながら、ゆるい感じに会話を進行してください。 `; //",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f3c",
      "text": " window.open(\"https://chatgpt.com/?temporary-chat=true&q=\"+encodeURIComponent(prompt),\"_blank\",\"popup,width=800,height=600\");",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f3d",
      "text": "   \t}",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f3e",
      "text": " });",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f40",
      "text": "code:script.js",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f41",
      "text": "  // 他のエージェントも追加する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f42",
      "text": "  function convertCosense(input, to = 'markdown') {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f43",
      "text": "      const lines = input.split('\\n');",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f44",
      "text": "      return lines.map(line => {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f45",
      "text": "          const bulletMatch = line.match(/^([ \\t\\u3000]+)/);",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f46",
      "text": "          if (bulletMatch) {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f47",
      "text": "              const indentStr = bulletMatch[1];",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f48",
      "text": "              const level = [...indentStr].length;",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f49",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f4a",
      "text": "              if (to === 'markdown') {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f4b",
      "text": "                  line = line.replace(/^([ \\t\\u3000]+)/, '  '.repeat(level) + '- ');",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f4c",
      "text": "              } else {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f4d",
      "text": "                  line = line.replace(/^([ \\t\\u3000]+)/, '　'.repeat(level) + '・');",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f4e",
      "text": "              }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f4f",
      "text": "          }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f50",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f51",
      "text": "          return line.replace(/\\[\\* (.+?)\\]/g, (_, p1) =>",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f52",
      "text": "              to === 'markdown' ? `**${p1}**` : p1",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f53",
      "text": "          ).replace(/\\[\\/+ (.+?)\\]/g, (_, p1) =>",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f54",
      "text": "              to === 'markdown' ? `*${p1}*` : p1",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f55",
      "text": "          ).replace(/\\[_+ (.+?)\\]/g, (_, p1) =>",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f56",
      "text": "              to === 'markdown' ? `<u>${p1}</u>` : p1",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f57",
      "text": "          ).replace(/\\[(https?:\\/\\/[^\\s\\]]+)\\s+(.+?)\\]/g, (_, url, text) =>",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f58",
      "text": "              to === 'markdown' ? `[${text}](${url})` : text",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f59",
      "text": "          ).replace(/\\[(.+?)\\s+(https?:\\/\\/[^\\s\\]]+)\\]/g, (_, text, url) =>",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f5a",
      "text": "              to === 'markdown' ? `[${text}](${url})` : text",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f5b",
      "text": "          ).replace(/\\[(https?:\\/\\/[^\\s\\]]+)\\]/g, (_, url) =>",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f5c",
      "text": "              to === 'markdown' ? `<${url}>` : url",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f5d",
      "text": "          ).replace(/(?<!\\[)(https?:\\/\\/[^\\s\\]]+)(?!\\])/g, (_, url) =>",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f5e",
      "text": "              to === 'markdown' ? `<${url}>` : url",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f5f",
      "text": "          ).replace(/\\[([^\\[\\]]+?)\\.icon\\]/g, (_, p1) => `(${p1})`)",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f60",
      "text": "           .replace(/\\[([^\\[\\]]+?)\\]/g, (_, p1) => p1);",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f61",
      "text": "      }).join('\\n');",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f62",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
    {
      "id": "69afd3ea00000000003b9f63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773130730,
      "updated": 1773130730
    },
